  <summary date="2022-12-14T19:07:12Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Technology Assessment for Air Quality Management Act of 2022

This bill addresses air quality monitoring technology, including by requiring the Environmental Protection Agency to update its Air Sensor Toolbox with specified information and establish an Air Quality Technology Working Group to report on air quality monitoring systems.

The Government Accountability Office must inventory national air quality monitoring infrastructure by documenting specified elements, such as locations and populations near such monitors.</summary>
